snippet.title: Spiral Knights: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: SEGA is proud to present a game from developer Three Rings: Spiral Knights! Check out this free to play online adventure, learn more -- and get a chance to play the game before release -- at http://www.spiralknights.com/ .
